The 2.2 version of SystemC is compliant with the IEEE 1666 SystemC 
standard. The IEEE 1666 Language Reference Manual (LRM) is the 
official standard for the SystemC language. It is a very useful 
reference document for all SystemC users, and it can be freely 
downloaded it at the URL below:

    http://standards.ieee.org/getieee/1666/index.html 
